snippet.title: "Leave Me and Kourtney Alone, L*SER" Travis Barker Speaks To Scott Disick

Kourtney Kardashian and Scott Disick have been one of the most famous couples in reality TV. The two started dating in 2006. They have three children together and they have managed to have a platonic relationship even after they broke up way back in 2015. Most of their family members and friends thought that the two would get back together again but this was never the case since the two reality TV stars went on to date other people.
